properties.Name: CountrySubdivision
properties.Description:
The Country Subdivision definition is based upon ISO 3166-2 Country Subdivision Codes:

The standard defines codes for identifying the principal subdivisions (e.g., provinces or states) of all countries coded in ISO 3166-1.

Columns.Name: SubdivisionId

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a FIPS Code.

Columns.Name: CountryId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Country.

Columns.Name: StateId
